mial distribution</a> that the hypergeometric distribution has to the binom=
ial distribution=E2=80=94the multinomial distribution is the "with-replacem=
ent" distribution and the multivariate hypergeometric is the "without-repla=
cement" distribution.
</p><p>The properties of this distribution are given in the adjacent table,=
