<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Application_to_auditing_ele=
ctions">Application to auditing elections</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection=
"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wiki=
