        <mn>5</mn>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mn>47</mn>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle 52-5=3D47}</a=
nnotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/eb3e7717ee3a9a320853fcba194466f49314fe0b" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.505ex; width:11.751ex; height:2.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle 52=
-5=3D47}"></span> still unseen.
</p><p>The probability that one of the next two cards turned is a club can =
be calculated using hypergeometric with <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe=
-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml=
-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/=
